 GENERAL:

   ESC             exit help / menus
   ALT+ENTER       toggle fullscreen

 PRESETS:

   SPACE / H       soft / hard cut to next preset
   BACKSPACE       go back to previous preset
   SCROLL LOCK     [un]lock current preset
   R               toggle random/sequential preset order 
   L               load specific preset
   M               show/hide preset-editing Menu
   S               save new preset
   A               do random mini-mash-up
   D               toggle warp & comp shader locks

 INFO:

   F1    help            F3    song time
   F2    song name       F4    preset name   

 PLAYBACK:

   F5    play/pause      F6    stop
   F7    prev            F8    next
   F9    shuffle         F10   repeat mode
   F11   volume up       F12   volume down